WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Antaeus Coe: Alright, let me share my screen and we'll start on the dashboard.

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:09.200
Antaeus Coe: This is the home screen — everything at a glance, the overview page for the whole account.

3
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Antaeus Coe: Now let's add an employee. This is the new hire flow, starting with the offer letter.

4
00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:31.000
Bryce: Does the new hire get the onboarding packet with the I-9 and W-4 right away?

5
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:36.000
Antaeus Coe: Exactly — onboarding kicks off automatically, I-9, W-4, even E-Verify and the background check.

6
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Antaeus Coe: Over here is invoicing — each invoice has line items, and billing runs monthly.

7
00:00:55.500 --> 00:00:58.000
Bryce: Can we see a statement for a single charge?

8
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.000
Antaeus Coe: And that's the demo. Any questions?
